sentences: Thana Alexa (born Thana Alexa PaveliÄ‡; born March 19, 1987) is a Croatian American jazz vocalist, composer, arranger and producer.
Thana Alexa and husband/ collaborator Antonio Sanchez shared the cover of DownBeat Magazine in the May 2020 issue.
For four consecutive years, Alexa has also appeared in the DownBeat magazine Critics' Poll for Rising Female Vocalist.
She was runner-up in the 2014 Made in New York Jazz Competition.
